{"tid":929783,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣氹掂個friend","createTime":"2018-12-05T23:10:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-09T13:22:31.000Z","uid":225428,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"809945c372e49aec00be07b886a334ecc68e95da","tid":929783,"uid":225428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T23:10:22.000Z","msg":"話說我有個相識10年既好兄弟，我地啱啱個暑假就因為一件好小既事炒左。佢就因為咁就幾個禮拜冇同我講野，之後我就主動搵佢想傾掂佢但係自己衰脾氣臭，又同佢吵，我地又炒炒地。<br />\n<br />\n之後我地終於出黎面對面傾左好耐，自問覺得可以做既都做左，道歉都道歉埋。正當我以為傾掂左（佢話佢唔嬲喇），今日我就聽到個mutual friend講話佢仲周圍同人講佢仲係唔妥我。<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔知點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都預左佢冇咁快會唔嬲但係我真係唔明點解兩個人嗌交，佢會寧願同人講佢唔妥我都唔直接同我傾<br />\n有冇人可以教我點樣可以拆點佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab37872667c1980e27b1ba4203942ec57fc4c1d7","tid":929783,"uid":146063,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T23:12:38.000Z","msg":"gay"},{"pid":"6df856eee8f4e139a47abcae4daa295482bf12e0","tid":929783,"uid":198165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T23:28:00.000Z","msg":"因為小學雞"},{"pid":"3b75840c9a6de9d8ed0dfc05dc257c1d2839ef3a","tid":929783,"uid":217416,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T23:30:31.000Z","msg":"識咗10年都仲會為小事嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bea8749c77ba6c8313e679cb66df1495a6963c07","tid":929783,"uid":113412,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T23:31:46.000Z","msg":"小事係導火線，應該積埋積埋唔少野"},{"pid":"539edbbd7ba79ea95462bfa554ed8af6f4564924","tid":929783,"uid":44364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T23:35:28.000Z","msg":"你唔講晒發生左咩事, 點樣應你??<br />\n有啲野真係可以嬲